  "StockRole": "Ultralight Scout",
  "YangsThoughts": "Clan Diamond Shark built these out of their Twycross factory after they rebuilt it. Ultralight scout, fifteen tons, not meant to fight anything seriously. Lyran Alliance bought most of them and mercenaries liked them too because they're cheap enough to risk losing. That Chameleon Light Polarization Shield is Star League era tech which is a nice touch for something this small. Don't let anyone shoot at it though.",
